pic/user/m/000/34/30/343003.jpg","floor":"#63-2","id":"1348135","time":"2018-5-18 19:46","userId":"yushenjushi","userName":"Leonhard Euler","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">花葬红蝶</span> 说: 哈哈哈，一个200部动画都没看完，还说请作豚远离的人好意思觉得自己很牛逼，否定和他审美差异很大的人的水平，真是笑死我了。</q></div>嘛，我看过多少动画你知道了？我倒是很好奇你哪里来的自信觉得我点的格子数就是看过的全部？至于其他的，显然你不是我表达的合格对象。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/04/60/46002.jpg","floor":"#64","id":"1347519","time":"2018-5-16 18:40","userId":"crest","userName":"全自动共产主义实现箱","userSign":"(May the force be with you.)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/61.gif\" smileid=\"100\" alt=\"(bgm84)\"><br>你用的也是B(angumi)站平分系统啊","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/07/310722.jpg","floor":"#65","id":"1347524","time":"2018-5-16 19:10","userId":"maple_5233","userName":"桜小路ルナ","userSign":"(大変に気分がいい)","message":"圈地自萌","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/90/309098.jpg","floor":"#66","id":"1348129","time":"2018-5-18 19:02","userId":"309098","userName":"Arclight","userSign":"","message":"Eva 9.7分，我只说一句<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/95.gif\" smileid=\"134\" alt=\"(bgm118)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/53/315316.jpg","floor":"#67","id":"1348136","time":"2018-5-18 19:54","userId":"yikaicheng","userName":"泽渡真琴","userSign":"(好大的关东煮)","message":"一个摇曳露营8.2的网站，人家还觉得不可思议呢","sub":[]}]